{"tid":1683813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月11號 全港一連三日大罷工 全力文宣 堅持落去","createTime":"2019-10-30T20:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T01:17:54.000Z","uid":134033,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2672204fad5e6046182b56bb1b4167f9db765f5","tid":1683813,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:45:38.000Z","msg":"相信各位手足心水都清 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即使去到如此黑暗既時代<br />\n<br />\n成個香港都未準備好全民勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真正夠膽出去以命攬炒 我估全港唔到二十個人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">既然當刻呢個方法唔可行<br />\n<br />\n請停止一切互屌 分化 灰心行為<br />\n<br />\n用實質行動去証明  追求自由既決心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 為左尊重番現有既行動 手足既付出<br />\n<br />\n參考番最新日程表  決定11號開始呢場罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">十日時間既文宣 未知係咪足夠 可能係小弟無腦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">幾個月以來發生既種種事  流過既血與淚<br />\n<br />\n失去左既前程 手腳 生命 寶貴既自由<br />\n<br />\n破碎左既家庭  所愛之人受到傷害<br />\n<br />\n再加上出盡奶力既文宣  <br />\n<br />\n都無辦法換來三日既真罷工<br />\n<br />\n對唔住</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下次會再做得更好 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日唔開槍打死哂我地 <br />\n<br />\n抗爭都會持續落去  <br />\n<br />\n沒有退路與失敗  只有自由與勝利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或許去到呢刻  大家都失去左方向<br />\n<br />\n變得迷惘 不知所措 進退兩難  灰心喪志<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但千奇唔好放棄  懶惰到唔再去行動<br />\n<br />\n堅持落去  勇和一體  絕不退讓<br />\n<br />\n不論一年 兩年 定十年<br />\n<br />\n追求自由民主既火種 永不熄滅<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">既然8月5號成功罷到一日<br />\n<br />\n我地就會罷到兩日 三日 更可能係一星期<br />\n<br />\nIt always seems impossible until it's done<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多  <br />\n<br />\n各位手足 堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d077c4dd72ae941bfef54aae466952fa9235b7","tid":1683813,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:48:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5987563fb1ff7618ecb4cace5cbca9221d65175b","tid":1683813,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:50:53.000Z","msg":"仆街 d排版咁柒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649ff1796c4c239ae4bb417fa5cc6ccd9792fef1","tid":1683813,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2902745e6401f679e4ab6379de5d91e3cad7f145","tid":1683813,"uid":3287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:52:25.000Z","msg":"721 831 101<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1111大罷工</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a1bf907fd438791a9797380d79b1be0e4520bd0b","tid":1683813,"uid":3287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5987563fb1ff7618ecb4cace5cbca9221d65175b","tid":1683813,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:50:53.000Z","msg":"仆街 d排版咁柒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets